---
// TrustStrip.astro
// Core truths that combat the 5 homeowner objections.
---
<section class="bg-charcoal text-cream py-16 lg:py-24 border-y border-brass/20 relative z-20 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 lg:gap-8">
      
      <!-- Objection 1: Will you show up? -->
      <div class="flex flex-col group">
        <div class="mb-6 text-brass group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform origin-left duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl mb-3 leading-tight">We've shown up every day since 1950.</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed">
          Over 5,000 projects. Not one abandoned. Our reputation is 75 years old. We're not going anywhere.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Objection 2: Who are these people in my house? -->
      <div class="flex flex-col group">
        <div class="mb-6 text-brass group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform origin-left duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
             <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl mb-3 leading-tight">You'll know exactly who's on your job.</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed">
          We don't use subcontractors. The crew you meet at the estimate is the crew that does the work.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Objection 3: Is the low bid a trap? -->
      <div class="flex flex-col group">
        <div class="mb-6 text-brass group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform origin-left duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl mb-3 leading-tight">We'll never be the cheapest quote.</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed">
          Contractors who win on price cut corners &mdash; materials, prep, insurance. We itemize everything before we touch a wall.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Objection 4: What happens if something goes wrong? -->
      <div class="flex flex-col group">
        <div class="mb-6 text-brass group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform origin-left duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            <!-- Note: Switched to badge-check / handshake concept -->
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8.94 13.52c-1.12.38-1.94 1.4-1.94 2.6V18c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h6c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2v-1.88c0-1.2-.82-2.22-1.94-2.6l-1.04-.34a4 4 0 0 1-2.48-2.4l-.24-.7A2.99 2.99 0 0 0 8.94 13.52zM12 9a3 3 0 1 0 0-6 3 3 0 0 0 0 6z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl mb-3 leading-tight">We warranty our work. In writing.</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed">
          We've been at this address for 75 years. If something isn't right, we come back and fix it. That's not a policy &mdash; it's how a family business survives three generations.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
